init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look down, and see a tiny bee, dressed in a tiny suit and hat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I am your loyal servant, your majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Then go and sting that man who has been bothering me."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "That one over there, the one with the red hat."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And with that, the bee flew off.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I could get used to this," she said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee returned, and said "Your Majesty, I have done as you commanded, and stung the man with the red hat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Now, go and sting every other man in the kingdom."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, Your Majesty, but I cannot do that.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, Your Majesty, but there are no more bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "What do you mean, no more bees?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Then go and find me a man with a stinger!"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was about to give the bee a piece of her mind, when she noticed that the bee was gone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, Your Majesty, but I cannot help you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The queen was moved by the bee's words.
